{
  "id": "adv_card_yu_11_03",
  "title": "鈴村優 3話 ドキドキしとったんは、うちだけ",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_office-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "env_adv_3d_office-01-000-noon",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――後日",
      "translations": {
        "en": "—Later",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-in-single-02.m4a",
          "delay": 2066.6666667000004,
          "startTime": 2.0666666667
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_11_03/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_11_03-yu001.m4a",
      "text": "なぁなぁ{user}さん！\nもし恋、完成したって聞いたんやけど、ホンマに？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hey‚ {user}-san!\nI heard Moshikoi is finished. Is that true?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 3.7,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_11_03/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_11_03-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "ああ、今日ちょうどテストプレイ用に届いたよ\nチェックも兼ねて――",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yeah‚ the test-play build arrived today.\nI was just about to check it—",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 11.5,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_11_03/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_11_03-yu002.m4a",
      "text": "遊びます！　遊ばせていただきます！\nちょっと会議室借りますね！！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I’m playing it! I will be playing it!!\nI’ll go borrow a meeting room!!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 15.9333333333,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_run-in-single-02.m4a",
          "delay": 3999.9995548999987,
          "startTime": 16.4333333333
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_11_03/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_11_03-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "お、おい優……って、行ってしまった\n凄い食い気味だったな。……でもなんで会議室？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "H-hey‚ Yu… she’s already gone.\nShe really jumped on that… But why a meeting room?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 23.7,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――二時間後",
      "translations": {
        "en": "—Two hours later",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 30.3876194636,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-in-single-02.m4a",
          "delay": 1512.3805363999984,
          "startTime": 31.9
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_11_03/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_11_03-yu003.m4a",
      "text": "はぁ……尊かった……あかん、しんど過ぎる……\nこんなん、全人類がうちに恋してまうやんか……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Haaah… it was so precious… I can’t… it was too much…\nStuff like this will make the whole world fall in love with me…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 40.6,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_11_03/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_11_03-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "そんなに面白かったのか\n出来映えはかなり良かったみたいだな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You liked it that much?\nSounds like the quality turned out really well.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 47.7333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_11_03/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_11_03-yu004.m4a",
      "text": "良かったどころじゃないです、最高傑作です！\n『優』の本心隠しがちで不器用な焦れったさも……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "“Really well” doesn’t cut it. It’s a masterpiece!\nYu’s awkward fumbling to hide her true feelings…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 54.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_11_03/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_11_03-yu005.m4a",
      "text": "主人公君のふと見せる強さも、二人の関係性も\n全部がエモの極み！　キュンの満漢全席！！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "The protagonist’s sudden bursts of strength‚ their whole dynamic—\nIt was peak emotion! A full-course meal of swoon!!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 63.3333353679,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_11_03/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_11_03-yu006.m4a",
      "text": "会議室の大画面でプレイしてて正解やったな……ふへへ\n人様に見せられんぐらい悶絶してもうたし……じゅる",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Playing it on the big meeting-room screen was the right choice… heheh.\nI was writhing so hard I couldn’t let anyone see me… drool…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 73.5000020345,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_11_03/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_11_03-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "……ゆ、優？　大丈夫か？\nまぁ、楽しかったのは何よりだけど",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Y-Yu? Are you okay?\nWell‚ I’m glad you had fun at least.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 82.1333353679,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_11_03/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_11_03-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "そうだ、先方にも優の所感を伝えておきたくてな\n具体的にどのシーンが良かったか教えてほしい",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Oh right—I want to share your impressions with the dev team.\nCan you tell me which scenes were especially good?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 90.2000020345,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_11_03/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_11_03-yu007.m4a",
      "text": "全部良かった！！　……ってのが本心やけど\nそうですね、具体的には……やっぱここです！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Everything!! …is the honest answer‚ but—\nLet’s see… specifically… yeah‚ this part!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 98.5412906414,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_11_03/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_11_03-yu008.m4a",
      "text": "このシーン、めっちゃこだわったシーンやからね！\n実際のゲームシーン見て声出てもうたわ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I put my heart into this scene!\nI actually screamed when I saw it in-game!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 110.1650928475,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_11_03/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_11_03-yu009.m4a",
      "text": "無防備な状態でこない美人が急に迫ってきたら\nメロメロになって落ちてまうのは確定やもん！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "If a beauty comes at you like that when you’re defenseless‚\nanyone would melt and fall for her instantly!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 118.3333353679,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_11_03/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_11_03-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "主人公とお忍びでクリスマスデートをするシーンか\n確かにここの不意打ちにはドキッとさせられるな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Oh‚ the incognito Christmas date scene with the protagonist.\nYeah‚ the surprise moment there is pretty heart-stopping.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 126.7333353679,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_11_03/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_11_03-yu010.m4a",
      "text": "せやろせやろ！？　しかもこのデート回は\n二人の関係性にまつわる大きな転換点",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Right‚ right!? And that whole date episode\nis a major turning point in their relationship!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 134.3333353679,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_11_03/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_11_03-yu011.m4a",
      "text": "キュンあり、笑いあり、ほんのりビターもありの\n次のシーンのカタルシスに向けた準備段階……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It’s a setup for the next scene’s catharsis‚\nwith swoons‚ laughs‚ a touch of bitters…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 142.6000020345,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_11_03/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_11_03-yu012.m4a",
      "text": "そんな大事なシーンでのご褒美イベントやもん！\n二重三重の意味でドキドキしてまうな！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "A bonus event in such a crucial moment!\nIt makes my heart race in more ways than one!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 150.5566875458,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_11_03/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_11_03-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "そ……そうだな。同意はするよ\nけど……さっきからちょっと、密着し過ぎじゃないか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Y-yeah… I agree.\nBut… aren’t you standing a bit too close to me?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 160.1333353679,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_11_03/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_11_03-yu013.m4a",
      "text": "うん？　……ああ、ゲームじゃなくて今ですか？\nふふっ、そんなん気にしてはるんですか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Huh? …Oh‚ you mean right now‚ not in the game?\nFufu‚ does that bother you?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 170.5333353679,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_11_03/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_11_03-yu014.m4a",
      "text": "{user}さん、ホンマは嬉しいくせに\nそれとも……もう、慣れてもうた？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You’re actually happy about it‚ aren’t you‚ {user}-san?\nOr… have you gotten used to it already?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 179.0666687012,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_11_03/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_11_03-yu015.m4a",
      "text": "ウブな{user}さんが垢抜けて\nからかい甲斐も誘惑のし甲斐もなくなってもうて……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "The innocent‚ flustered {user}-san is all grown-up now…\nNo fun to tease or seduce anymore…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 185.5000020345,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_11_03/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_11_03-yu016.m4a",
      "text": "だとしたらうち、寂しいわぁ……\n……な～んて。ふふっ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "If that’s the case‚ I’d be so lonely…\n…Just kidding. Fufu.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 194.5666687012,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_11_03/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_11_03-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "まったく……そうやって大人をからかうんじゃない",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Seriously… don’t tease adults like that.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 197.3666694005,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_11_03/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_11_03-yu017.m4a",
      "text": "は～い。……でもこの仕上がりなら、バッチリやな\nファンのみんなも、喜んでくれたらええなぁ……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Okaaay. …But with this quality‚ it’s perfect.\nI hope all the fans will love it too…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 207.3000020345,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――『もし恋』リリースイベント当日",
      "translations": {
        "en": "—Moshikoi Release Event Day",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 211.2666694005,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stagesleeves-00-noon",
      "startTime": 212.9666778564
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stagesleeves-00-noon",
      "startTime": 213.0666778564
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_11_03/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_11_03-yu018.m4a",
      "text": "{user}さん、今日のうちの衣装どうです？\nめっちゃ似合ってると思わへん？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "{user}-san‚ how’s my outfit today?\nDon’t you think it suits me perfectly?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 217.8000020345,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
