      "text": "怜ちゃん達の時も思ったけど\nゲーム内の衣装を完全再現って……ホンマに凄いな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I thought the same back at Rei-chan’s event‚\nbut recreating in-game outfits perfectly… it’s amazing.",
