      "text": "ゲーム自体も好評な中でのリリースイベントだからな\n気絶はともかく、度肝は抜かれるだろうな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Well‚ the game’s already popular before release‚ so…\nMaybe not faint‚ but they’ll definitely be stunned.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 245.1929233477,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
