      "text": "渚ちゃんはドラマチックな内容に泣いた言うてて\n瑠依ちゃんはうちのストーリーテリングも褒めてくれて",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Nagisa-chan said she cried at the dramatic parts‚\nRui-chan even praised my storytelling.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 261.0666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stagesleeves-00-noon",
      "startTime": 264.9666775385
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
