      "text": "別にうちがシナリオ本文を書いた訳やないのにな\nそんな褒められると、逆に申し訳ないわ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Even though I didn’t actually write the script.\nGetting praised that much almost makes me feel guilty.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 269.4070483366,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stagesleeves-00-noon",
      "startTime": 273.5333442051
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
